  Locus:
    Page: 455
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
To be born is to suffer; to grow old is to suffer; to die is to suffer; to
be tied to what is not loved is to suffer; to endure what is distasteful is
to suffer. In short, all the results of individuality, of separate self-
hood, necessarily involve pain or suffering.
